Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_BA
Enum.Value: Delivery cannot be completed without better address information

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_CA
Enum.Value: Receiver's business premises were closed and delivery could not be completed

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_CD
Enum.Value: Shipment's process has been delayed because import, export or transit clearance processing requirements cannot be completed due to a reason that has been agreed to be within DHL's control

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_CM
Enum.Value: Consignee is no longer at the delivery address shown on the piece label or waybill

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_DM
Enum.Value: Damage to all or part of the shipment or packaging. May or may not result in a service failure

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_HP
Enum.Value: Shipment and its associated piece(s) are on hold at a DHL facility pending payment of any applicable fees, and that the outbound processing or the delivery has not as yet been attempted.

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_IA
Enum.Value: Images of shipment paperwork have been made available to the network

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_MC
Enum.Value: A piece has been received at a DHL facility with an incorrect service area code shown on the piece label

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_MD
Enum.Value: A shipment has missed the current courier delivery cycle

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_MS
Enum.Value: A piece has been incorrectly sorted despite the correct destination service area code present on both the piece label and/or the package

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_NA
Enum.Value: A pre-alerted shipment has not physically arrived on the advised linehaul movement

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_ND
Enum.Value: A piece was with a delivery courier but delivery has not been attempted or completed and no other service incident applies

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_OH
Enum.Value: The progress of a piece has been suspended, and that the piece is being held securely at a DHL facility until progress can continue

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_RD
Enum.Value: The receiver has refused to accept delivery of the piece

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_SC
Enum.Value: A change in service has been made to a shipment in transit

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_TD
Enum.Value: A delay has occured to a piece, shipment or handling unit during transport between two DHL facilities. This may or may not affect the Service Commitment for each individual shipment

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_TI
Enum.Value: A trace has been initiated against a shipment or piece

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_TT
Enum.Value: A trace has been terminated against a shipment or piece

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_UD
Enum.Value: A shipment's progress has been delayed because import, export or transit clearance-processing requirements cannot be completed due to a reason that has been agreed to be outside DHL'S control

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_BR
Enum.Value: The transfer of responsibility for a shipment, all associated pieces and related documentation, to a customer nominated Broker

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_CS
Enum.Value: A shipment is missing after all standard efforts have been made to locate it, it may also denote that a shipment has never physically been collected or received or signify the closing of a mis-coded shipment

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_DD
Enum.Value: the receiver has accepted delivery of a piece but considers the piece damaged or contents missing at time of delivery

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_DS
Enum.Value: A piece has been destroyed or disposed of in accordance with the appropriate DHL global standard operating procedure

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_OK
Enum.Value: the successful delivery of a piece at the time of delivery handover

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_RT
Enum.Value: A piece is being returned for a specific reason to the sender or DHL origin

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_SS
Enum.Value: A shipment's progress has been stopped or seized by an official government authority and that the shipment will not be delivered or returned to DHL

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_TP
Enum.Value: A third party will deliver a piece. No delivery details are expected

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_HK
Enum.Value: The shipment has been collected from shipper and scanned by DHL

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_AD
Enum.Value: A piece is held at the destination service centre and is awaiting its expected and agreed delivery date, e.g. Public Holiday or for pieces where a pre-agreed delivery date or schedule has been made

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_AF
Enum.Value: The arrival of a piece at a DHL transit facility or combined (Hub/GTW and service centre) facility

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_AR
Enum.Value: The arrival of a piece at the destination delivery facility

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_BL
Enum.Value: The location of a piece as it is placed into a regulatory control bond

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_BN
Enum.Value: Customer's broker has been contacted to arrange for the clearance of the shipment

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_CC
Enum.Value: The piece is awaiting receiver collection at a DHL location as per customer request

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_CI
Enum.Value: A piece has been received into a facility or a specific point in the process

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_CR
Enum.Value: Shipment's release from clearance processing or from a bonded area

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_CU
Enum.Value: A piece or handling unit uplift  by a movement operator has been confirmed to DHL. This may or may not affect the service commitment for each shipment

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_DF
Enum.Value: the departure of a shipment from the control of a DHL Facility

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_DI
Enum.Value: A shipment has had a duty invoice raised against it during clearance and that fees (duties and / or taxes) will be payable on or before delivery

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_ES
Enum.Value: A customs entry has been submitted for clearance of a shipment

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_FD
Enum.Value: The hand over of a piece to a third party delivery agent where delivery details are expected. May also be used for regionally approved remote DHL service areas where deliveries will not be attempted until the next business day or greater

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_HI
Enum.Value: A piece has been lodged into the held inventory control area

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_HO
Enum.Value: A piece held in inventory status has been resolved and the piece is ready to be taken out for further processing

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_IC
Enum.Value: A declarable shipment is under routine clearance processing

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_PD
Enum.Value: A delivery has been made and signed for, but not for all pieces of a shipment

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_PL
Enum.Value: One of a number of processes: The containerisation of a piece, The assigning of one handling unit to another, The assigning of a handling unit to a movement or the reporting of piece/shipment/handling unit handover between couriers.

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_PU
Enum.Value: The physical receipt of a shipment from a shipper

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_RR
Enum.Value: Customs has provided or updated a status for a house waybill declaration which has been submitted to customs

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_RW
Enum.Value: A piece has had its weight and/or dimensions captured

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_SA
Enum.Value: The physical acceptance of a piece by an agent or when dropped off by a customer to a service point

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_SD
Enum.Value: Shipment data has been received into the tracking system

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_SI
Enum.Value: A shipment inspection (content and/or security) related event has been conducted by DHL or an assigned agent for shipment acceptability and/or security purposes

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_SM
Enum.Value: A piece is now scheduled to move on a specified date and time

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_ST
Enum.Value: A special handling instruction has been raised against a piece, shipment or handling unit

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_TR
Enum.Value: The tranfer of a piece outside a DHL facility in an unopened positively containerised handling unit.

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_WC
Enum.Value: A piece has been allocated to a delivery route and that a delivery attempt will soon be made with delivery details expected on the same day

Enum.Name: DeliveryStatus_YY
Enum.Value: A shipment has been passed directly to a sorting hub, without receiving a scan
